PrecisAppointment of the Honourable ROGER CHOUINARD, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Quebec, as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of Quebec, who shall, during pleasure, execute the office and functions of the LIEUTENANT GOVERNOR of QUEBEC during the absence, illness or other inability of the Lieutenant Governor, effective March 17, 1993.
